<h1>Articles</h1>

Our blog has <%= Article.count %> articles:
  <%= Article.public_count %> <strong>public</strong>,
  <%= Article.private_count %> <strong>private</strong>,
  <%= Article.archived_count %> <strong>archived</strong>

<ul>

  <% @articles.each do |article| %>

    <% unless article.archived? %>

      <li>
        <%= link_to article.title, article %>
      </li>

    <% end %>

  <% end %>

</ul>

<%= link_to "New Article", new_article_path %>
